replies.body:
He actually has a good bit of flexibility,
It's just very subtile.
All of his spell can be used in both an offensive and defensive manner:
You can Use his Q to engage, run, or nuke;
His spell shield has a million and one uses;
Unspeakable horror can either hold a champion down or to force someone chasing you to disengage;
His ult can be an initiation or an execution, and if you're in a bind the vision block can cover your escape or bluff an enemy into backing down.

Nocturne is a very flexible champion, he just requires a lot of thought and timing to function as such.
